    "- Loki datasource configured in Grafana",
    "- Promtail scraping Docker container logs",
    "",
    "PROMTAIL CONFIGURATION:",
    "Promtail is configured to scrape Docker logs from /var/lib/docker/containers/",
    "with job label 'containerlogs'",
    "",
    "QUERY: {job=\"containerlogs\"}",
    "",
    "NOTES:",
    "- Simple log viewer for all Docker containers across all LXC hosts",
    "- Use Grafana's log panel filters for searching",
    "- Filter by container_name, host, or stream labels",
